al and commercial, construction, transport and other sectors in the implementation of independent economic accounting management and organization in some cities by industry professional management organization, also known as the company. With the reform of China's economic sy";}i:5;a:9:{s:2:"id";s:1:"6";s:5:"title";s:6:"新闻";s:4:"sort";s:1:"6";s:4:"link";s:21:"http://www.baidu.com/";s:5:"photo";s:17:"571050cd87652.jpg";s:8:"headline";s:6:"新闻";s:13:"distriibution";s:411:"新闻，是指通过报纸、电台、广播、电视台、互联网等媒体途径所传播信息的一种称谓。新闻概念有广义与狭义之分。就其广义而言，除了发表于报刊、广播、互联网、电视上的评论与专文外的常用文本都属于新闻之列，包括消息、通讯、特写、速写（有的将速写纳入特写之列）等等，狭义的新闻则专指消息。";s:9:"eheadline";s:4:"news";s:14:"edistriibution";s:500:"News, the title refers to a dissemination of information through newspapers, radio, radio, television, Internet and other media channels. News concept has broad and narrow sense. Its broad terms, in addition to publication in the press, radio, Internet, TV reviews and monographs on the outside of the common text of the news belong to the column, including messages, communications, close-up, sketch (sketch included in the close-up of some of the columns), etc. et al., refers specifically to narro";}}}
